title: Cross Section of Gamma-Rays Production At Inelastic Interaction of 14 Mev Neutrons With Different Nuclei.

x4freetext: CROSS SECTION OF GAMMA-RAYS PRODUCTION AT INELASTIC
INTERACTION OF 14 MEV NEUTRONS WITH DIFFERENT NUCLEI.

x4codes.hlp: Institut Atomnoi Energii I.V. Kurchatova, Moskva, Union of Soviet Socialist Republics

x4freetext: DATA ARE GIVEN.
ABSOLUTE MEASUREMENT.
TIME OF FLIGHT METHOD WITH TIME RESOLUTION 15
NSEC. ENERGY RESOLUTION FOR 1.12 MEV GAMMA RAYS IS
10 PERCENT.
COCKROFT-WALTON ACCELERATOR
SOLID SCINTILLATOR (NA I)
DEUTERON-TRITIUM
GAMMAS
HOLLOW SPHERE WITH OUTER DIAMETER 7 CM
CORRECTION IS MADE ON DETECTOR EFFICIENCY
DETECTOR EFFICIENCY ERROR IS 7 PERCENT. NEUTRON
FLUX  UNCERTAINTY IS 3 PERCENT. UNCERTAINTY OF NEUTRON
AND OF GAMMAS ABSORPTION IN SAMPLE IS 2-3 PERCENT.ERROR
OF CALCULATION OF RESOLUTE PART OF SPECTRUM IS 5-10
PERCENT. ERROR OF CALCULATION OF NONRESOLUTE PART OF
SPECTRUM IS 10-20 PERCENT. STATISTICAL ERROR IS 2-5
PERCENT. TOTAL ERROR IS 10-40 PERCENT.
COMPILED AT CENTRE
SOME ERRORS CORRECTED
